02:54.360 --> 02:57.989
JOB OPPORTUNITIES

03:10.320 --> 03:14.552
- Last place of employment?
- Denver, Colorado.

03:14.760 --> 03:18.992
I worked there for ten years...
but then things just dried up.

03:20.240 --> 03:24.119
They lost 14 banks in one week.

03:30.200 --> 03:33.556
There's nothing available for you,
right now.

03:42.120 --> 03:47.911
They use their tongues to
deceive you. Venom is on their lips.

03:48.120 --> 03:54.116
Their mouths are full
of bitterness and curses.

03:54.320 --> 03:58.472
The fear of God
is not before their eyes.

03:58.680 --> 04:06.439
They have taken
the hearts and minds of our leaders.

04:06.640 --> 04:09.632
They have blinded us to the truth.

04:09.840 --> 04:15.676
Our human spirit is corrupted.
Why do we worship greed?

04:15.880 --> 04:21.591
Outside the limit of our sight
they're feeding off us.

04:21.800 --> 04:28.353
Perched on top of us
from birth to death, are our owners.

04:28.560 --> 04:33.236
They have us. They control us.
They are our masters.

04:33.440 --> 04:37.194
Wake up.
They're all around you.

05:01.640 --> 05:08.113
<i>Sometimes when I watch TV</i>
<i>I stop being myself. I'm a star. </i>

05:08.320 --> 05:13.952
<i>I have my own talk show. Or I'm</i>
<i>on the news getting out of a limo. </i>

05:14.160 --> 05:19.109
<i>All I ever have to do is be famous. </i>
<i>People watch me. </i>

05:19.320 --> 05:22.676
<i>And they love me. </i>

05:22.880 --> 05:28.273
<i>I never grow old, and I never die. </i>

05:46.440 --> 05:49.432
Excuse me,
do you need anybody?

05:51.080 --> 05:54.755
- Maybe.
- I've got my own tools.

05:55.640 --> 05:59.519
This is a union job.

06:04.320 --> 06:11.749
May I please speak
with the shop steward, sir?

06:46.560 --> 06:51.554
There's no sleeping on this site.
Sleep somewhere else tonight.

06:51.760 --> 06:55.753
Excuse me, when do I get paid?

06:55.960 --> 06:58.394
Thursday.

07:10.160 --> 07:13.038
Do you need a place to stay?

07:13.240 --> 07:19.679
There's a place over on 4th street.
They've got hot food and showers.

07:47.040 --> 07:50.953
I don't like being followed
unless I know why.

07:51.160 --> 07:56.712
I don't turn up with anybody
until I see where he's going.

08:18.080 --> 08:21.755
They'll be serving food up soon.

08:32.960 --> 08:39.149
This is Gilbert. Anything you need,
he knows where to find it.

08:40.520 --> 08:43.432
- What's in the pack, tools?
- Yes, sir.

08:43.640 --> 08:49.192
If you can use them,
you can fix the shower over there.

08:49.400 --> 08:52.597
Let's get something to eat.

09:10.640 --> 09:14.349
- More?
- Yeah.

09:22.080 --> 09:26.312
I've got a wife and two kids
back in Detroit.

09:26.520 --> 09:30.593
I haven't seen them in six months.

09:30.800 --> 09:36.636
The steel mills were laying people off.
They finally went under.

09:38.440 --> 09:45.278
We gave the steel companies a break.
They gave themselves pay raises.

09:46.760 --> 09:51.959
The golden rule: He who has the gold
makes the rules.

09:55.480 --> 10:00.918
If they close one more factory, we
should take a sledge to their foreign cars.

10:01.120 --> 10:05.989
- You should have more patience.
- I'm all out.

10:07.440 --> 10:11.513
The whole deal
is some kind of crazy game.

10:11.720 --> 10:16.271
The name of the game is:
Make it through life.

10:16.480 --> 10:22.828
Only everyone is out for themselves
and looking to do you in.

10:23.040 --> 10:29.479
You do what you can, but I'm going
to do my best to blow your ass away.

10:34.840 --> 10:41.279
- So how are you going to make it?
- My chance will come.

10:41.480 --> 10:45.678
I believe in America.
I follow the rules.

10:46.720 --> 10:51.430
Everybody has got
their own hard times, these days.

11:12.800 --> 11:18.750
<i>You thought press-on nails would</i>
<i>impede all the active things you do. </i>

11:18.960 --> 11:24.193
<i>We've got beautiful, natural-Iooking, </i>
<i>easy-to-apply nails. </i>

11:24.400 --> 11:28.313
<i>There's seven different colors... </i>

11:29.840 --> 11:32.559
<i>Our impulses are being redirected. </i>

11:32.760 --> 11:38.039
<i>We live in an artificially-induced</i>
<i>state of consciousness. </i>

11:38.240 --> 11:43.109
Goddamn hacker. That's the second
time tonight that asshole has cut in.

11:43.320 --> 11:47.871
<i>The movement began eight months ago</i>
<i>by a group of scientists. </i>

11:48.080 --> 11:53.029
<i>They accidentally discovered</i>
<i>these signals being sent... </i>

11:56.040 --> 11:59.112
That thing's giving me a headache.

11:59.320 --> 12:02.949
It must have taken him months
to figure out how to do this.

12:03.160 --> 12:09.429
<i>The under-class is growing. </i>
<i>Human rights are non-existent. </i>

12:09.640 --> 12:17.194
<i>In their repressive society, we</i>
<i>are their unwitting accomplices. </i>

12:18.680 --> 12:23.800
<i>Their intention to rule rests with</i>
<i>the annihilation of consciousness. </i>

12:24.000 --> 12:30.678
<i>We have been lulled into a trance. </i>
<i>They have made us indifferent. </i>

12:30.880 --> 12:36.193
<i>We are focused</i>
<i>only on our own gain... </i>

12:43.560 --> 12:48.315
<i>They are safe</i>
<i>as long as they are not discovered. </i>

12:48.520 --> 12:53.878
<i>That is their method of survival. </i>
<i>Keep us asleep. Keep us selfish. </i>

12:54.080 --> 12:59.473
<i>- Keep us sedated. </i>
- Blow it out of your ass.

14:21.520 --> 14:27.709
- Choir practice was late last night.
- The church lets us use their kitchen.

14:29.280 --> 14:34.877
- Till four in the morning?
- We care for a lot of people here.

14:43.520 --> 14:49.914
<i>The sleeping middle-class</i>
<i>is suddenly becoming poor. </i>

14:50.120 --> 14:56.036
<i>We are their cattle. </i>
<i>We are being bred for slavery. </i>

14:56.920 --> 15:02.278
- Not again.
<i>- We cannot break their signal. </i>

15:02.480 --> 15:07.793
<i>The signal must be shut off</i>
<i>at the source. </i>

15:08.000 --> 15:10.912
- I have a headache.
- Me too, honey.

15:14.520 --> 15:20.038
- What was that all about?
- That idiot's licking his nuts again.

16:49.880 --> 16:53.236
THEY LIVE WE SLEEP

17:07.119 --> 17:09.839
There's nothing wrong with it.

17:12.000 --> 17:15.675
Only a few seconds got on the air.

17:15.880 --> 17:20.510
Forget about breaking their signal.
They justjam us out again.

17:20.720 --> 17:27.068
- Put the shipment out on the street.
- It won't work. We've discussed this.

17:27.280 --> 17:30.158
We have no other choice.

17:37.680 --> 17:44.119
Robbing banks. Making our own lenses.
We just can't reach enough people.

17:52.760 --> 17:55.433
We've got to find strong people
who'll work with us.

18:23.600 --> 18:28.993
I'm just leaving. Your door was open.
I just thought I'd close it.

18:29.200 --> 18:34.513
- Neighborhood watch.
- Let me touch your face.

18:34.720 --> 18:37.837
Now your hands.

18:38.040 --> 18:42.511
You're a working man.
The revolution...

18:42.720 --> 18:48.078
- Let me show you.
- Maybe some other time.

18:49.040 --> 18:54.114
This world may have blinded me,
but the Lord let me see.

18:54.320 --> 18:57.471
You'll be back.

19:13.280 --> 19:18.832
I've been hearing stuff on the street.
Weird stuff.

19:19.040 --> 19:22.396
An epidemic of violence
is what they're saying.

19:22.600 --> 19:26.149
I was talking
to one old boy from San Anselmo.

19:26.360 --> 19:32.435
He says up there they're talking
end-of-the-world kind of stuff.

19:47.040 --> 19:51.238
- What are they doing?
- Shooting people, robbing banks.

19:51.440 --> 19:58.198
A whole lot of people going crazy
over some nutty dream they just had.

20:00.920 --> 20:05.869
The truth is, this kind of shit
happens at the end of every century.

20:06.080 --> 20:10.153
It's just people
afraid to face the future.

20:18.840 --> 20:21.354
What's happening?

20:21.560 --> 20:27.669
I was inside there. It's full of boxes
and some kind of lab setup.

20:27.880 --> 20:31.998
- What do you mean?
- The singing is a tape recording.

20:34.440 --> 20:39.070
Leave it alone, man.
It's none of our business.

20:39.280 --> 20:42.795
Gilbert is in there helping them.

20:47.640 --> 20:52.794
I've got ajob now.
I just keep walking the white line.

20:53.000 --> 20:58.393
I don't bother nobody. Nobody bothers
me. You should do the same.

21:05.080 --> 21:11.155
The line in the middle of the road.
That's the worst place to drive.

21:14.280 --> 21:18.956
- I'll see you later.
- See you later.

22:04.080 --> 22:08.517
Step down. Easy. This way.

22:12.800 --> 22:16.918
Now we cross the road.
It's dirt here.

22:55.480 --> 22:57.152
Go, go!

24:36.160 --> 24:38.151
Frank!

25:22.560 --> 25:27.998
Leave us alone.
We know you.

25:40.720 --> 25:46.795
"Though I walk through the valley of
the shadow of death, I fear no evil."

27:12.400 --> 27:17.076
- Come and join the party.
- You go with them.

27:35.400 --> 27:38.836
Did somebody start WW III?

28:02.080 --> 28:08.076
<i>Oman's collection</i>
<i>puts passion before fashion. </i>

28:08.280 --> 28:12.478
<i>Out goes glitter</i>
<i>and in comes divine excess. </i>

28:12.680 --> 28:20.519
<i>The warm collection revels</i>
<i>in freedom of expression. </i>

31:06.480 --> 31:09.233
